OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Flikely through the evening for many
OL,7,Fparts. Cloudier in the south, with
OL,8,Fsporadic light rain expected.
OL,9,FTemperatures in the clearer skies
OL,10,Fquickly falling overnight, with frost
OL,11,Flikely in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FVariable cloud, with good
OL,14,Fspells of sunshine for the morning.
OL,15,FSome patchy rain possible for the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
